{"tid":115562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民協肥議員江貴生搭巴士偷拍靚模斷正","createTime":"2017-02-10T15:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T18:00:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7084329c49916a9242c7c754d497cb884016bc","tid":115562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170210/56285196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170210%2F56285196&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=73549224\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170210%2F56285196&h=f38cc9d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170210/56285196</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170210/large/1486703137_312b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170210%2Flarge%2F1486703137_312b.jpg&h=c288f69e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】<br />\n𡃁模Isis Lee本月4日在facebook上載一幅往元朗巴士車廂內拍攝相片，相中有一位四眼男子持手機兼戴耳筒，視線望側邊，Isis留言指「呢個肥哥哥全程268c個幾鐘一直晌度偷拍我訓覺，我望住佢佢仲要扮打機！你背後塊玻璃反光我睇到曬！你個Mon係我張相！妖，人哋收工累了上車訓覺你都要影！痴漢！變態架！」引發網路公審，其後該男子被揭是民協區議員江貴生，激起雙方支持者的對罵。江貴生出聲明否認，並自嘲「外型肥毒宅」，暗指事主不應基於他人的樣貌或體型而妄斷。但事主Isis網上逐點反駁江及支持江的網民質疑，重申親眼見到從巴士車窗反光見到江的手機mon上，有其車上睡覺的相片，不過沒有拍到此情況。"},{"pid":"4a3607e7f722957d6e7142c00a6fa540dbd537bf","tid":115562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s29.postimg.org/514uxfkxj/ISIS_Lee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs29.postimg.org%2F514uxfkxj%2FISIS_Lee.jpg&h=60197971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主Isis指江「真係欺人太甚！佢當時見事敗即逃按鐘落車，又唔見佢提及下？佢走我點即時捉住佢呀？清者自清，應該係由我講先啱！我真係好後悔當時無衝出去同車長講，希望各位女仕借鏡」。"},{"pid":"aefc1f37172a8ed3433c1cea1f9da4bdfb1aecfd","tid":115562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"民協成個黨都極麻甩核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20150621/s00125/1434824350652_4327A221BA4B7C6900EE7C67A2EF1CB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20150621%2Fs00125%2F1434824350652_4327A221BA4B7C6900EE7C67A2EF1CB4.jpg&h=9003b955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b145aeffc51f6128341b5657a9ee73b2ff2c26bb","tid":115562,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報警都唔識"},{"pid":"238d46dfa831aab89546212fc9722d65597262e2","tid":115562,"uid":5482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"臭雞搏上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdc469d8cb86d4b92d12df1bf19a3e0a9901332","tid":115562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"民協改名做痴漢黨啦"},{"pid":"b2e478dbc40ccb2a49578b8c8c7de821fc4163cf","tid":115562,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"唔理邊個講真邊個講假<br />\n<br />\n條女就黑仔架啦今次<br />\n<br />\n又無證據 又影中個區議員<br />\n<br />\n而家仲上埋跑 告你誹謗你都硬食 因為你完全無任何證據"},{"pid":"8d3f6bec74126e6018569472717ee75c0f5cbe05","tid":115562,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"重申親眼見到從巴士車窗反光見到江的手機mon上，有其車上睡覺的相片，不過沒有拍到此情況。<br />\n<br />\n無圖你話咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4db9b251c117e0f2cf3fd9cb6843abcea4d5b1","tid":115562,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"事主lsis 差啲睇左做isis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b09799c1e6cebe5a2c36c37046940b9952450b5","tid":115562,"uid"